{"tid":1108895,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"實況主「塗黑臉」Cos Apex Lifeline，遭 Twitch 判定歧視被 Ban 台","createTime":"2019-04-16T06:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T16:07:41.000Z","uid":185134,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d644d8bf9eca011e0c594266db8d40dffba038c3","tid":1108895,"uid":185134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/gJjoWFpxWRAA2cRR7q2Bkw--~A/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz01MjY7aD0zMzE-/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/78fbb6b3e5e3af25ae8c8d831b30fba4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgJjoWFpxWRAA2cRR7q2Bkw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz01MjY7aD0zMzE-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F78fbb6b3e5e3af25ae8c8d831b30fba4&h=04e99ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKarupups 是位來自立陶宛的 Twitch 實況主 Coser，在上週末（14日）她實況進行《APEX 英雄》（APEX Legends）的輔助型角色「生命線」角色扮演，展現角色扮演這門技術的難度，包括妝感、道具、服裝等等，最後她開始將臉塗黑，在最後化妝還未完成前，她的 Twitch 頻道就遭到封鎖而停止直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/IQ8IgOcfaNW63XZjAtRegA--~A/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz02MjI7aD00Mzc-/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/e8e417b2395c082378168dea86fc3d47\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIQ8IgOcfaNW63XZjAtRegA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz02MjI7aD00Mzc-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fe8e417b2395c082378168dea86fc3d47&h=2294ac61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受到 Twitch 30 天的 Ban 台處罰，Karupups 透過 YouTube 影片再次澄清自己並沒有種族歧視的意思並強調：「我只是盡全力讓自己更像《Apex》的生命線，這並不代表我在嘲笑任何人。她是我在遊戲裡最喜歡的一位角色，這只是種 Cosplay。」<br />\n社群反應兩極，有人認為這是美國強加自身文化到其他地區身上，是管得太多，也有人認為，在美國這是實質存在的歷史問題，規定上也有寫到明文禁止， Twitch 是美國公司，那就照他們當地的法律管理。<br />\n<br />\n在美國文化中被視為「blackface」，也就是將臉塗成黑人膚色的種族歧視行為，在歷史上是實際存在的一段歧視歷史，對美國而言相當嚴重，2月就發生過維吉尼亞州長，因為他的畢業紀念冊的照片最後下台。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LooPbW-OZhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLooPbW-OZhU&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd1wLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=03be4b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LooPbW-OZhU</a><br />\n遊戲圈內類似的事件在 2017 年曾經發生過，當時韓國的 Coser Pion 扮演《鬥陣特攻》（Overwatch）「駭影」時，為了角色完成度，選擇把皮膚塗得更黑，同樣引發部分批評。<br />\n<br />\n好撚惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔cosplay得黑人角色"},{"pid":"80e2efe8e11bbb7fddf617412968aca07cdaf75e","tid":1108895,"uid":4525,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"7497f84c2212e08054e98267d769d8dc8a564192","tid":1108895,"uid":200328,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"白人cosplay黑人角色都歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb633c25ef6086a79834d55dafc4bd0a70dab0c3","tid":1108895,"uid":7043,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"黑人玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd48d8a9f3ed3e2ea8f263de036c22644acaf9b","tid":1108895,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"條女好正下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177a043a27e64f346fef27f76e6b78956d9090ac","tid":1108895,"uid":165361,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"果D 肥腫黑人cos 白人/黃種人角色,點計先<br />\nsailor moon,嗚門...."},{"pid":"391492ea1d4307b66b3fac8904b399052109959c","tid":1108895,"uid":155177,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同支那人一撚樣 低智商<br />\n有咩事就大叫THIS IS RACISM"},{"pid":"149a9b84cc336bdbff5d359d22067572941bd7ed","tid":1108895,"uid":80103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco